  <h2>Translation and Localization Tools</h2>

  <h3>Machine Translation</h3>

  <p>Major machine translation platforms now offer variant-aware Portuguese translation:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Google Translate:</strong> Offers Brazilian and European Portuguese as distinct language options</li>
    <li><strong>DeepL:</strong> Provides Portuguese translation with variant considerations</li>
    <li><strong>Microsoft Translator:</strong> Supports Portuguese with regional awareness</li>
  </ul>

  <p>However, users should be aware that machine translation between variants remains imperfect. The tools work best for content conversion between Portuguese and other languages rather than between variants.</p>

